1
00:00:01,160 --> 00:00:06,110
Hey, guys. Do you feel
like we're being watched?

2
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:07,410
[ALL]
Huh?

3
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:12,490
Are we live?

4
00:00:12,570 --> 00:00:15,570
Oh. Hello, hello,
my little cubbies!

5
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:18,660
And welcome to your favorite
Fairy Fox's livestream!

6
00:00:18,740 --> 00:00:21,990
So today, we've got a package
from a fellow cultivator!

7
00:00:22,070 --> 00:00:26,200
Oh! And this one
comes from Li Chao!

8
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:28,240
Thanks so much, my cubby wubby!

9
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:31,490
Now who's ready to rip it open
and see what's inside?

10
00:00:31,570 --> 00:00:32,700
[CHEN CHAO giggles]

11
00:00:32,780 --> 00:00:35,490
[FAIRY FOX]
Huh. I don't know what it is.

12
00:00:35,570 --> 00:00:38,660
Tongue of the Heavenly
Hound medicine?

13
00:00:38,740 --> 00:00:41,490
[chuckles]
So, you like it, Fairy Fox?

14
00:00:41,570 --> 00:00:44,740
How's your master been
feeling today? Any better?

15
00:00:44,820 --> 00:00:46,950
[FAIRY FOX gasps] Thank you
for asking, my friend.

16
00:00:47,030 --> 00:00:48,240
On behalf of my master,

17
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,780
I want you to know I
appreciate you, but...

18
00:00:50,860 --> 00:00:52,820
...he's still
unconscious in the ICU,

19
00:00:52,910 --> 00:00:54,990
so I wish I had better news.

20
00:00:55,070 --> 00:00:57,950
However, thanks to your kind and
thoughtful donation of medicine,

21
00:00:58,030 --> 00:01:00,660
I think my master will
feel better real soon!

22
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:02,450
[CHEN CHAO] I'll do everything
I can to help you

23
00:01:02,530 --> 00:01:03,700
in your time of need.

24
00:01:03,780 --> 00:01:04,990
[FAIRY FOX] I don't know
what I'd do without you.

25
00:01:05,070 --> 00:01:06,530
You've been so generous.

26
00:01:06,610 --> 00:01:09,360
How could I possibly repay
you for your kindness?

27
00:01:09,450 --> 00:01:11,990
If it's okay with you,
I was thinking maybe

28
00:01:12,070 --> 00:01:15,610
we could have a private chat,
just the two of us?

29
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:20,200
[shouts]

30
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:26,240
♪

31
00:03:14,530 --> 00:03:16,820
[ZHUO YI] Ancestral leaders
of the past, thank you

32
00:03:16,910 --> 00:03:20,070
for coming out of retirement
to be here, all of you.

33
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:22,030
Well, why are we here?

34
00:03:22,110 --> 00:03:25,660
Must be of great importance,
to summon us old retirees.

35
00:03:25,740 --> 00:03:28,780
The world's total energy has
dropped to four point seven.

36
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:30,490
We've got a crisis on our hands.

37
00:03:30,570 --> 00:03:33,030
[MALE PREDECESSOR B] The same
thing happened last year!

38
00:03:33,110 --> 00:03:36,200
So what? You gathered
us all up for that?

39
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:39,360
Not quite. The spirit shell
protecting the world

40
00:03:39,450 --> 00:03:42,410
has weakened because
of the low energy.

41
00:03:42,490 --> 00:03:45,070
In its fragile state,
a spatial crack has formed,

42
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,530
enabling demon spies
to infiltrate our world.

43
00:03:47,610 --> 00:03:51,570
I've got an easy solution.
We could just build a wall.

44
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:55,360
A huge one. Frankly, I alone
can revive the energy

45
00:03:55,450 --> 00:03:57,610
and then make the
human race great again!

46
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:59,860
[MALE PREDECESSOR D] We know
exactly what the demons want!

47
00:03:59,950 --> 00:04:02,700
They've had their greedy eyes
on our world for an eternity,

48
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:04,860
and they're willing to go
to war to take it from us!

49
00:04:04,950 --> 00:04:07,110
[MALE PREDECESSOR C]
Hmph. That is fake news!

50
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:10,490
Trust me, I know demons!
A lot better than you!

51
00:04:10,570 --> 00:04:14,160
You idiot! You think building
a wall will stop 'em?

52
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,570
We must take initiative
and strike them first!

53
00:04:16,660 --> 00:04:20,410
Gentlemen, we don't know the
demon world coordinates.

54
00:04:20,490 --> 00:04:22,320
If we attempt to find it now,

55
00:04:22,410 --> 00:04:24,610
we could get lost
in spatial storms.

56
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,320
[MYSTERIOUS PREDECESSOR A]
Why bother?

57
00:04:26,410 --> 00:04:29,070
We could capture a demon
and interrogate them.

58
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,990
Problem solved.

59
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:32,490
[MALE PREDECESSOR C]
The demons are good people,

60
00:04:32,570 --> 00:04:34,280
just get in there
and make a deal.

61
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,200
They won't do anything reckless.

62
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:38,700
[MALE PREDECESSOR D] You know,
when you put it that way,

63
00:04:38,780 --> 00:04:42,910
maybe we should keep
our ideas to ourselves.

64
00:04:42,990 --> 00:04:45,660
[sighs]
Why'd they go offline?

65
00:04:47,910 --> 00:04:50,280
[GUO HAO]
Wang Ling. Come on!

66
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:53,660
Hello! Earth to Wang Ling!

67
00:04:53,740 --> 00:04:54,570
What's wrong?

68
00:04:54,660 --> 00:04:56,280
It's Chen Chao.

69
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,990
His dad's here and
he's really pissed off!

70
00:04:59,070 --> 00:04:59,910
Huh?

71
00:04:59,990 --> 00:05:03,780
[STUDENTS chatter]

72
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:05,410
[GUO HAO grunts]
'scuse us.

73
00:05:05,490 --> 00:05:07,530
[MALE STUDENT B]
Huh?

74
00:05:07,610 --> 00:05:10,740
Stupid boy. What's the
matter with you?

75
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:13,660
Why have you dropped
down a phase?

76
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:16,070
Well, father, one of the
lessons you taught me

77
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:19,240
as a child was to be
kind and help others.

78
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:22,570
And as fate would have it,
I found someone that needs help.

79
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:26,070
Her master was hurt so bad that
he's unconscious in the ICU,

80
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,780
and now she spends
her time livestreaming

81
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:29,200
to raise money for him.

82
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:31,660
You gave your energy
to this temptress,

83
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:34,280
all in an effort to
save her master?

84
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,280
[CHEN CHAO]
Yes, father!

85
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:39,910
[FATHER CHEN]
Hm... You know what they say.

86
00:05:39,990 --> 00:05:42,740
Good deeds will always
trump good intentions,

87
00:05:42,820 --> 00:05:47,320
reckless or not. You did
this for someone in need.

88
00:05:47,410 --> 00:05:51,410
I am happy those family
lessons were taken to heart.

89
00:05:51,490 --> 00:05:52,820
You may keep your phone.

90
00:05:52,910 --> 00:05:55,360
[CHEN CHAO gasps]
Thanks, father!

91
00:05:56,740 --> 00:05:58,860
[FATHER CHEN] While I'm here,
do you happen to know

92
00:05:58,950 --> 00:06:02,110
where our family's Tongue
of the Heavenly Hound is?

93
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,740
[CHEN CHAO]
Uh, well.

94
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:06,030
[FAIRY FOX] Since Li Chao
sweetly gifted this Tongue

95
00:06:06,110 --> 00:06:07,490
of the Heavenly Hound,

96
00:06:07,570 --> 00:06:11,610
today I'll return the favor
with a special live chat!

97
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:14,070
It's not what you think.
Sir, please let me explain.

98
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,530
[FATHER CHEN]
Enough!

99
00:06:15,610 --> 00:06:18,240
You didn't care about her
master's well-being at all.

100
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:20,610
You did this to impress her.

101
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:22,700
Stupid boy, you're gonna
pay for this!

102
00:06:22,780 --> 00:06:23,570
[CHEN CHAO yelps]

103
00:06:23,660 --> 00:06:25,780
[ALL gasp]

104
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:29,200
[CHEN CHAO whimpers]

105
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,990
[CHEN CHAO]
Fairy Fox!

106
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:38,530
If I see you watching
another live stream,

107
00:06:38,610 --> 00:06:40,780
you'll lose more
than your phone.

108
00:06:44,860 --> 00:06:45,910
[SUN RONG]
What's wrong with him?

109
00:06:45,990 --> 00:06:47,530
And how did watching
a livestream

110
00:06:47,610 --> 00:06:48,820
knock him down a phase?

111
00:06:48,910 --> 00:06:51,530
We live in the
seven-twenty-nine-G era now.

112
00:06:51,610 --> 00:06:52,950
The bandwidth is so insane,

113
00:06:53,030 --> 00:06:56,030
it even supports donations
of spiritual energy!

114
00:06:56,110 --> 00:06:59,160
Uh. You can donate,
but not that much.

115
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,700
It's witchcraft.

116
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:01,990
Witchcraft?

117
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:04,820
Long ago, demons would
disguise themselves

118
00:07:04,910 --> 00:07:08,660
as pretty women and then
drain their victim's energy,

119
00:07:08,740 --> 00:07:11,410
leaving their bodies
frail and disabled.

120
00:07:11,490 --> 00:07:14,610
I'm guessing Chen Chao was
seduced by the dark arts.

121
00:07:14,700 --> 00:07:16,240
[SUN RONG]
How do you know all this?

122
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,780
[XIAOYU LIN] Oh, I dunno.
I guess I've always been

123
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:21,990
fascinated by the
more obscure magic.

124
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,410
Guys, he's fine.

125
00:07:23,490 --> 00:07:25,490
When his Dad embarrassed
him in front of the school,

126
00:07:25,570 --> 00:07:26,820
he learned his lesson.

127
00:07:26,910 --> 00:07:30,240
[CHEN CHAO laughs]

128
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:32,450
--[GUO HAO] Huh?
--[XIAOYU LIN gasps]

129
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:37,240
[FAIRY FOX yawns] Welcome back
to the livestream,

130
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,660
my little Li Chao!

131
00:07:38,740 --> 00:07:41,110
Why'd you go offline and
leave me all alone?

132
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:44,450
Eh, dealing with family stuff.
Nothing bad.

133
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:48,700
[SUN RONG sighs]
That boy's a lost cause.

134
00:07:48,780 --> 00:07:50,820
You think a demon's
involved somehow?

135
00:07:50,910 --> 00:07:52,240
That would make sense.

136
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:54,910
Is there any way to
break the spell?

137
00:07:54,990 --> 00:07:57,490
The quickest way is to
use a meta spirit.

138
00:07:57,570 --> 00:08:00,570
Once inside the internet,
they find the demon's location

139
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:03,240
and disrupt their dark arts.

140
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:06,660
This method requires someone at
a golden pill phase or higher.

141
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:08,160
And, if they're powerful enough,

142
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,610
they could even transfer
their physical body.

143
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:12,780
[GUO HAO]
You guys can sit back and relax.

144
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:15,490
Infecting the demon's channel
should do the trick.

145
00:08:15,570 --> 00:08:16,490
[GUO HAO chuckles]

146
00:08:16,570 --> 00:08:18,950
Ooh! I love it! What is it?

147
00:08:19,030 --> 00:08:22,700
[GUO HAO] You mean Trojan?
She's my digital spirit beast.

148
00:08:22,780 --> 00:08:25,740
I've raised her for years.
Now it's time to shine!

149
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:29,030
And all I need to do is type
in the stream's web address.

150
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:34,570
Be free! Go get'em, girl!

151
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:36,280
[TROJAN neighs]

152
00:08:43,410 --> 00:08:48,320
[gasps] Hm! There you are.
You can't hide from me.

153
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,530
[TROJAN neighs]

154
00:08:52,610 --> 00:08:55,700
[FIREWALL A laughs]

155
00:08:55,780 --> 00:08:56,990
[ALL gasp]

156
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:03,570
[FIREWALL A laughs]

157
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:08,030
Trojan, no!

158
00:09:13,110 --> 00:09:14,490
[FAIRY FOX giggles]

159
00:09:14,570 --> 00:09:16,950
Whoops, just had a little
technical issue pop up,

160
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:18,450
but I hope you're still with me.

161
00:09:18,530 --> 00:09:20,570
Are you ready for
our voice chat?

162
00:09:20,660 --> 00:09:23,160
[CHEN CHAO]
Oh, you know I'm ready!

163
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,410
[SUN RONG]
Look at him.

164
00:09:24,490 --> 00:09:26,990
He's drained so much,
he looks like a corpse.

165
00:09:27,070 --> 00:09:30,530
If his father sees this,
he's gonna be in big trouble.

166
00:09:30,610 --> 00:09:32,570
[WANG LING]
Hm. Thank you.

167
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:38,360
What about Little Wise Guy?

168
00:09:38,450 --> 00:09:41,030
Right! We could use
a mind trick on him!

169
00:09:41,110 --> 00:09:42,530
What's that?

170
00:09:42,610 --> 00:09:45,200
[SUN RONG] It's an art of
seduction we learned last year.

171
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,700
I've used it on
Chen Chao before,

172
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,700
and it worked a little too well.

173
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:52,990
Oh, yeah! Out seduce her.
Fighting fire with fire!

174
00:09:53,070 --> 00:09:54,410
Exactly!

175
00:09:54,490 --> 00:09:57,490
[FAIRY FOX gasps] Oh my gosh,
you sound so young!

176
00:09:57,570 --> 00:09:59,030
Did you graduate yet?

177
00:09:59,110 --> 00:10:01,280
Not yet. I'm 18.

178
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,570
[FAIRY FOX gasps]

179
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:04,990
Hey, Chen Chao.
You want something to drink?

180
00:10:05,070 --> 00:10:07,240
Yeah, thanks.

181
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:10,070
[FAIRY FOX gasps] Wow, you
didn't say you had a girlfriend!

182
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:14,110
Oh no, she's just
another classmate.

183
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,740
Wouldn't want ya to
get the wrong idea.

184
00:10:15,820 --> 00:10:19,410
Oh, just another
classmate, huh?

185
00:10:21,490 --> 00:10:23,780
That's it! He took the offering!

186
00:10:23,860 --> 00:10:29,530
It's time! Not giving a part
of me to benefit the world.

187
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:32,990
[FEMALE ANNOUNCER A]
Warning. Warning.

188
00:10:33,070 --> 00:10:35,820
You have lost your connection
with Target Two-fifty.

189
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:37,820
Popularity falling.

190
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:41,660
I'm right here.
Please come back to us.

191
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:45,360
We're really worried about you.

192
00:10:45,450 --> 00:10:47,200
You're right, guys. I'm sorry.

193
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,070
[FAIRY FOX gasps]

194
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:51,160
Fairy Fox, I'm going offline.

195
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:54,780
[gasps]
Aw, Chaochao.

196
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:57,700
Do you really have
to leave me so soon?

197
00:10:57,780 --> 00:11:00,320
]This is the first time
I've chatted with a fan,

198
00:11:00,410 --> 00:11:02,700
and it feels great.

199
00:11:02,780 --> 00:11:05,610
I can't thank you enough
for helping with my master.

200
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:09,740
Because of your kindness, I just
had the best day of my life.

201
00:11:09,820 --> 00:11:12,160
[SUN RONG]
What is she trying to do?

202
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:17,240
My only wish is that this moment
could have lasted forever,

203
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,740
but I understand you've
gotta get out there

204
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:22,820
and go live your life.

205
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:25,200
[whimpers]
I know what's happening.

206
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:28,490
You're leaving 'cause I'm
not popular enough for you.

207
00:11:28,570 --> 00:11:32,530
I can return your gifts,
but it breaks my heart.

208
00:11:32,610 --> 00:11:36,490
My biggest regret is not
meeting you sooner.

209
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:37,490
[CHEN CHAO]
Hm!

210
00:11:37,570 --> 00:11:39,570
[SUN RONG]
Oh no, he's gonna break!

211
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:43,200
Listen to me! Don't give in!
You gotta snap out of it!

212
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:45,700
Please don't leave me!

213
00:11:45,780 --> 00:11:48,820
--[SUN RONG gasps]
--[CHEN CHAO grunts]

214
00:11:50,070 --> 00:11:52,110
[SUN RONG shouts]

215
00:11:53,990 --> 00:11:56,700
We're done. Behave yourself.

216
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:02,160
[MALE ANNOUNCER A]
You lose!

217
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:07,660
[FAIRY FOX]
Hm! The plan's working.

218
00:12:07,740 --> 00:12:10,360
Just a bit more,
and we're good to go!

219
00:12:10,450 --> 00:12:13,950
Master, we'll have you up
and moving in no time.

220
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:15,160
[CHEN CHAO grunts]

221
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,070
[FAIRY FOX]
Four spirit-powered mini-TVs?

222
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:19,490
Aw, you shouldn't have!

223
00:12:19,570 --> 00:12:24,240
[XIAOYU LIN] Not Sun Rong, too!
What are we gonna do!

224
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:27,780
[FATHER CHEN] Son, whatever
you've done, it's a sin.

225
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:30,200
[XIAOYU LIN yells]

226
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:32,570
[FATHER CHEN] When I was
his age, my hormones took me

227
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:36,820
on wild adventures as well and
I was just as stubborn, too.

228
00:12:38,530 --> 00:12:40,740
The ancient Tongue of
the Heavenly Hound.

229
00:12:40,820 --> 00:12:43,410
My wife gave it to me
as a token of affection.

230
00:12:43,490 --> 00:12:46,030
That was long ago,
when we were dating.

231
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:47,700
It all makes sense now.

232
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:50,570
The apple doesn't fall
far from the tree!

233
00:12:50,660 --> 00:12:52,820
Karma is inevitable.

234
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:54,950
Good or bad, it all comes back.

235
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:57,450
What grievous sins have
my family committed

236
00:12:57,530 --> 00:13:00,360
to be trapped in this
endless cycle of depravity?

237
00:13:00,450 --> 00:13:03,360
[SUN RONG gasps]
It's okay.

238
00:13:03,450 --> 00:13:05,110
Wow, that was special.

239
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,360
A father connecting
with his son.

240
00:13:07,450 --> 00:13:10,240
Aw! We got a family
heirloom from Chaochao!

241
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:12,820
